{"id":167,"ayahs":[{"number":138,"arabic":"وَجَٰوَزْنَا بِبَنِىٓ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ ٱلْبَحْرَ فَأَتَوْا۟ عَلَىٰ قَوْمٍۢ يَعْكُفُونَ عَلَىٰٓ أَصْنَامٍۢ لَّهُمْ ۚ قَالُوا۟ يَٰمُوسَى ٱجْعَل لَّنَآ إِلَٰهًۭا كَمَا لَهُمْ ءَالِهَةٌۭ ۚ قَالَ إِنَّكُمْ قَوْمٌۭ تَجْهَلُونَ","translation":"AND WE BROUGHT the children of Israel across the sea; and thereupon they came upon people who were devoted to the worship of some idols of theirs. Said [the children of Israel]: \"O Moses, set up for us a god even as they have gods!\" He replied: \"Verily, you are people without any awareness [of right and wrong]!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1092.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":78862,"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَـٰوَزْنَا","translation":"আর পার করালাম আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78863,"position":2,"arabic":"بِبَنِىٓ","translation":"বনী","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78864,"position":3,"arabic":"إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ","translation":"ইসরাঈলকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78865,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْبَحْرَ","translation":"সমুদ্র","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78866,"position":5,"arabic":"فَأَتَوْا۟","translation":"অতঃপর তারা আসলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78867,"position":6,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78868,"position":7,"arabic":"قَوْمٍۢ","translation":"এক জাতির","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78869,"position":8,"arabic":"يَعْكُفُونَ","translation":"তারা পূজায় লেগে ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78870,"position":9,"arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78871,"position":10,"arabic":"أَصْنَامٍۢ","translation":"প্রতিমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78872,"position":11,"arabic":"لَّهُمْ ۚ","translation":"তাদের (নিমিত্ত)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78874,"position":12,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78875,"position":13,"arabic":"يَـٰمُوسَى","translation":"\"হে মূসা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78876,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱجْعَل","translation":"বানাও","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78877,"position":15,"arabic":"لَّنَآ","translation":"জন্যে আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78878,"position":16,"arabic":"إِلَـٰهًۭا","translation":"একটি দেবতা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78879,"position":17,"arabic":"كَمَا","translation":"যেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78880,"position":18,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তাদের (রয়েছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78881,"position":19,"arabic":"ءَالِهَةٌۭ ۚ","translation":"দেবতাসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78883,"position":20,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(মূসা) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78884,"position":21,"arabic":"إِنَّكُمْ","translation":"\"নিশ্চয়ই তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78885,"position":22,"arabic":"قَوْمٌۭ","translation":"(এমন)সম্প্রদায়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78886,"position":23,"arabic":"تَجْهَلُونَ","translation":"(যারা) মূর্খতা করছো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_138_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78887,"position":24,"arabic":"١٣٨","translation":"(১৩৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":139,"arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰٓؤُلَآءِ مُتَبَّرٌۭ مَّا هُمْ فِيهِ وَبَٰطِلٌۭ مَّا كَانُوا۟ يَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"As for these here -verily, their way of life is bound to lead to destruction; and worthless is all that they have ever done!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1093.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":79007,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79008,"position":2,"arabic":"هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ","translation":"এসব (লোক)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79009,"position":3,"arabic":"مُتَبَّرٌۭ","translation":"বিধ্বস্ত হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79010,"position":4,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79011,"position":5,"arabic":"هُمْ","translation":"তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79012,"position":6,"arabic":"فِيهِ","translation":"মধ্যে যার (লিপ্ত আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79013,"position":7,"arabic":"وَبَـٰطِلٌۭ","translation":"এবং ভ্রান্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79014,"position":8,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79015,"position":9,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","translation":"তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79016,"position":10,"arabic":"يَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"তারা কাজ করে আসছে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_139_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79017,"position":11,"arabic":"١٣٩","translation":"(১৩৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":140,"arabic":"قَالَ أَغَيْرَ ٱللَّهِ أَبْغِيكُمْ إِلَٰهًۭا وَهُوَ فَضَّلَكُمْ عَلَى ٱلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translation":"[And] he said: \"Am I to seek for you a deity other than God, although it is He who has favoured you above all other people?\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1094.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":79121,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(মূসা) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_140_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79122,"position":2,"arabic":"أَغَيْرَ","translation":"\"কি ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/007_140_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79123,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_140_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79124,"position":4,"arabic":"أَبْغِيكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্যে আমি খুঁজে বেড়াবো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_140_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79125,"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَـٰهًۭا","translation":"(অন্য) ইলাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_140_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79126,"position":6,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"অথচ তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_140_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79127,"position":7,"arabic":"فَضَّلَكُمْ","translation":"শ্রেষ্ঠত্ব দিয়েছেন তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_140_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79128,"position":8,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_140_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79129,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","translation":"বিশ্বজগতের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_140_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79130,"position":10,"arabic":"١٤٠","translation":"(১৪০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":141,"arabic":"وَإِذْ أَنجَيْنَٰكُم مِّنْ ءَالِ فِرْعَوْنَ يَسُومُونَكُمْ سُوٓءَ ٱلْعَذَابِ ۖ يُقَتِّلُونَ أَبْنَآءَكُمْ وَيَسْتَحْيُونَ نِسَآءَكُمْ ۚ وَفِى ذَٰلِكُم بَلَآءٌۭ مِّن رَّبِّكُمْ عَظِيمٌۭ","translation":"And [he reminded them of this word of God]: \"Lo, We saved you from Pharaoh's people who afflicted you with cruel suffering, slaying your sons in great numbers and sparing [only] your women - which was an awesome trial from your Sustainer.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1095.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":79237,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذْ","translation":"এবং (স্মরণ করো) যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79238,"position":2,"arabic":"أَنجَيْنَـٰكُم","translation":"আমরা উদ্ধার করেছিলাম তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79239,"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنْ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79240,"position":4,"arabic":"ءَالِ","translation":"অনুসারীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79241,"position":5,"arabic":"فِرْعَوْنَ","translation":"ফিরাউনের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79242,"position":6,"arabic":"يَسُومُونَكُمْ","translation":"যন্ত্রণা দিতো তোমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79243,"position":7,"arabic":"سُوٓءَ","translation":"নিকৃষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79244,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْعَذَابِ ۖ","translation":"শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79246,"position":9,"arabic":"يُقَتِّلُونَ","translation":"তারা হত্যা করতো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79247,"position":10,"arabic":"أَبْنَآءَكُمْ","translation":"পুত্রদেরকে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79248,"position":11,"arabic":"وَيَسْتَحْيُونَ","translation":"ও তারা জীবিত রাখতো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79249,"position":12,"arabic":"نِسَآءَكُمْ ۚ","translation":"নারীদেরকে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79251,"position":13,"arabic":"وَفِى","translation":"ও (ছিলো) মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79252,"position":14,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكُم","translation":"এর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79253,"position":15,"arabic":"بَلَآءٌۭ","translation":"পরীক্ষা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79254,"position":16,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"পক্ষ হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79255,"position":17,"arabic":"رَّبِّكُمْ","translation":"রবের তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79256,"position":18,"arabic":"عَظِيمٌۭ","translation":"বড়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_141_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79257,"position":19,"arabic":"١٤١","translation":"(১৪১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":142,"arabic":"۞ وَوَٰعَدْنَا مُوسَىٰ ثَلَٰثِينَ لَيْلَةًۭ وَأَتْمَمْنَٰهَا بِعَشْرٍۢ فَتَمَّ مِيقَٰتُ رَبِّهِۦٓ أَرْبَعِينَ لَيْلَةًۭ ۚ وَقَالَ مُوسَىٰ لِأَخِيهِ هَٰرُونَ ٱخْلُفْنِى فِى قَوْمِى وَأَصْلِحْ وَلَا تَتَّبِعْ سَبِيلَ ٱلْمُفْسِدِينَ","translation":"AND [then] We appointed for Moses thirty nights [on Mount Sinai]; and We added to them ten, whereby the term of forty nights set bye, his Sustainer was fulfilled. And Moses said unto his brother Aaron: \"Take thou my place among my people; and act righteously, and follow not the path of the spreaders of corruption.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1096.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":79334,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَوَٰعَدْنَا","translation":"এবং আমরা প্রতিশ্রুতি দিয়েছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79335,"position":2,"arabic":"مُوسَىٰ","translation":"মূসাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79336,"position":3,"arabic":"ثَلَـٰثِينَ","translation":"ত্রিশ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79337,"position":4,"arabic":"لَيْلَةًۭ","translation":"রাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79338,"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَتْمَمْنَـٰهَا","translation":"ও তা আমরা (বাড়িয়ে)পূর্ণ করি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79339,"position":6,"arabic":"بِعَشْرٍۢ","translation":"দিয়ে (আরও)দশ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79340,"position":7,"arabic":"فَتَمَّ","translation":"অতঃপর পূর্ণ হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79341,"position":8,"arabic":"مِيقَـٰتُ","translation":"নির্ধারিত সময়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79342,"position":9,"arabic":"رَبِّهِۦٓ","translation":"তাঁর রবের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79343,"position":10,"arabic":"أَرْبَعِينَ","translation":"(অর্থাৎ) চল্লিশ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79344,"position":11,"arabic":"لَيْلَةًۭ ۚ","translation":"রাত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79346,"position":12,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","translation":"ও বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79347,"position":13,"arabic":"مُوسَىٰ","translation":"মূসা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79348,"position":14,"arabic":"لِأَخِيهِ","translation":"উদ্দেশ্যে তার ভাইয়ের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79349,"position":15,"arabic":"هَـٰرُونَ","translation":"(অর্থাৎ) হারুণকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79350,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱخْلُفْنِى","translation":"\"আমার প্রতিনিধিত্ব করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79351,"position":17,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79352,"position":18,"arabic":"قَوْمِى","translation":"আমার জাতির","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79353,"position":19,"arabic":"وَأَصْلِحْ","translation":"এবং সংশোধন করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79354,"position":20,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79355,"position":21,"arabic":"تَتَّبِعْ","translation":"অনুসরণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79356,"position":22,"arabic":"سَبِيلَ","translation":"পথ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79357,"position":23,"arabic":"ٱلْمُفْسِدِينَ","translation":"বিপর্যয় সৃষ্টিকারীদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_142_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79358,"position":24,"arabic":"١٤٢","translation":"(১৪২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":143,"arabic":"وَلَمَّا جَآءَ مُوسَىٰ لِمِيقَٰتِنَا وَكَلَّمَهُۥ رَبُّهُۥ قَالَ رَبِّ أَرِنِىٓ أَنظُرْ إِلَيْكَ ۚ قَالَ لَن تَرَىٰنِى وَلَٰكِنِ ٱنظُرْ إِلَى ٱلْجَبَلِ فَإِنِ ٱسْتَقَرَّ مَكَانَهُۥ فَسَوْفَ تَرَىٰنِى ۚ فَلَمَّا تَجَلَّىٰ رَبُّهُۥ لِلْجَبَلِ جَعَلَهُۥ دَكًّۭا وَخَرَّ مُوسَىٰ صَعِقًۭا ۚ فَلَمَّآ أَفَاقَ قَالَ سُبْحَٰنَكَ تُبْتُ إِلَيْكَ وَأَنَا۠ أَوَّلُ ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"And when Moses came [to Mount Sinai] at the time set by Us, and his Sustainer spoke unto him, he said: \"O my Sustainer! Show [Thyself] unto me, so that I might behold Thee!\" Said [God]: \"Never canst thou see Me. However, behold this mountain: if it remains firm in its place, then - only then - wilt thou see Me. And as soon as his Sustainer revealed His glory to the mountain, He caused it to crumble to dust; and Moses fell down in a swoon. And when he came to himself, he said: \"Limitless art Thou in Thy glory! Unto Thee do I turn in repentance; and I shall [always] be the first to believe in Thee!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1097.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":79515,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَمَّا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79516,"position":2,"arabic":"جَآءَ","translation":"আসলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79517,"position":3,"arabic":"مُوسَىٰ","translation":"মূসা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79518,"position":4,"arabic":"لِمِيقَـٰتِنَا","translation":"মধ্যে আমাদের নির্ধারিত সময়ের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79519,"position":5,"arabic":"وَكَلَّمَهُۥ","translation":"ও তার সাথে কথা বললেন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79520,"position":6,"arabic":"رَبُّهُۥ","translation":"তাঁর রব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79521,"position":7,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79522,"position":8,"arabic":"رَبِّ","translation":"\"হে আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79523,"position":9,"arabic":"أَرِنِىٓ","translation":"আমাকে দেখা দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79524,"position":10,"arabic":"أَنظُرْ","translation":"(যেন) আমি দেখি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79525,"position":11,"arabic":"إِلَيْكَ ۚ","translation":"আপনার প্রতি\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79527,"position":12,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(আল্লাহ তা'লা) বললেন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79528,"position":13,"arabic":"لَن","translation":"\"কখনও না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79529,"position":14,"arabic":"تَرَىٰنِى","translation":"তুমি আমাকে দেখতে পারবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79530,"position":15,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِنِ","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79531,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱنظُرْ","translation":"তুমি লক্ষ্য করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79532,"position":17,"arabic":"إِلَى","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79533,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلْجَبَلِ","translation":"পাহাড়টির","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79534,"position":19,"arabic":"فَإِنِ","translation":"অতঃপর যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79535,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱسْتَقَرَّ","translation":"স্হির থাকে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79536,"position":21,"arabic":"مَكَانَهُۥ","translation":"তার জায়গায় (পাহাড়)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79537,"position":22,"arabic":"فَسَوْفَ","translation":"তবে শীঘ্রই\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_143_023.mp3","charTypeName":"